OL,3,CDelivery driver killed during van
OL,4,Ctheft 'paid ultimate price'
OL,6,FA parcel delivery driver who died as
OL,7,Fhe tried to stop his van from being
OL,8,Fstolen "paid an immensely high price"
OL,9,Ffor trying to prevent a crime, a
OL,10,Fcoroner has said.
OL,12,FClaudiu-Carol Kondor, 42, died at the
OL,13,Fscene in Heights Drive, Wortley,
OL,14,FLeeds, on 20 August after his silver
OL,15,FFord Transit Cargo van was stolen.
OL,17,FHe had been making a delivery in
OL,18,Fnearby Alliance Street when he
OL,19,Freturned to find a thief taking the
OL,20,Fvan.
