OL,4,Ctheft 'paid ultimate price'
OL,6,FOn Friday, an inquest into his death
OL,7,Fwas opened and adjourned at Wakefield
OL,8,FCoroners' Court by senior coroner
OL,9,FKevin McLoughlin.
OL,11,FMr McLoughlin said Mr Kondor, from
OL,12,FSheffield, was "a Romanian gentleman
OL,13,Fwho was contributing to society".
OL,15,FHe added: "He was here, he was working
OL,16,Fhard, when he found someone stealing
OL,17,Fhis vehicle.
OL,19,F"He's commendably tried to prevent the
OL,20,Fcrime taking place but he's paid an
OL,21,Fimmensely high price for this."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
