OL,6,FThe coroner said this was the "violent
OL,7,Fand unnatural death of a valued
OL,8,Fcitizen".
OL,10,FMr McLoughlin gave very brief details
OL,11,Fof how Mr Kondor found someone
OL,12,F"endeavouring to steal his vehicle"
OL,13,Fand was injured as he tried to
OL,14,Fintervene.
OL,16,FThe coroner said his cause of death
OL,17,Fwas head and chest injuries.
OL,19,FThe van was later found abandoned in
OL,20,FBelle Isle.
