OL,6,FHe described Mr Kondor's death as
OL,7,F"heartbreaking" and added: "My
OL,8,Fheartfelt sympathies go out to Mr
OL,9,FKondor's family."
OL,11,FNo members of Mr Kondor's family were
OL,12,Fin court for the short hearing and the
OL,13,Finquest was adjourned to a date to be
OL,14,Ffixed.
OL,16,FThe coroner said Mr Kondor was
OL,17,Fdelivering for Amazon at the time.
