OL,6,FHe was employed by a company called SP
OL,7,FTransport Group, who described him at
OL,8,Fthe time of the incident as "more than
OL,9,Fjust a colleague - he was a friend, a
OL,10,Fconfidant and a valued member of our
OL,11,Fteam".
OL,13,FMark Ross, 32, of Conference Road,
OL,14,FArmley, Leeds, appeared in court last
OL,15,Fmonth accused of murdering Mr Kondor.
OL,17,FHe is due to go on trial next year.
OL,19,FTwo other people were arrested in
OL,20,Fconnection with the incident.
