OL,6,FA 24-year-old man who was arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder was released on
OL,8,Fbail pending further inquiries and a
OL,9,Fwoman, who was arrested at the same
OL,10,Ftime on suspicion of assisting an
OL,11,Foffender, was released under
OL,12,Finvestigation.
OL,14,FAn online fundraiser set up to support
OL,15,FMr Kondor's family has collected more
OL,16,Fthan #31,000.
OL,18,FOrganiser Mike Neill said: "The
OL,19,Foverwhelming support, generosity, and
OL,20,Fkindness shown by so many has been
OL,21,Fnothing short of incredible.
